<section class="section-tight shell"><div class="two-column"><article class="card card-pad"><p class="eyebrow">Quick answers</p><h2 class="heading-card-lg">Most asked</h2><details open><summary>Can I buy or cash out Cozy Coins?</summary><div>Cozy Coins are not sold separately and cannot be transferred, redeemed, withdrawn, or exchanged for anything of value. Eligible memberships include a disclosed fixed daily play-money grant.</div></details><details><summary>Does membership improve odds?</summary><div>No. Membership can add a fixed number of daily Cozy Coins, but never changes probability, payout multipliers, theoretical return, or game rules.</div></details><details><summary>How do I take a break?</summary><div>Use the permanent Healthy Play link or <a href="<?= $url('take-a-break', [], '/take-a-break') ?>">Take a Break</a>. There is no penalty.</div></details><details><summary>Where are game probabilities?</summary><div>Each game page includes rules, paytable, and probability tabs. The <a href="<?= $url('probabilities.index', [], '/probabilities') ?>">probability library</a> collects them.</div></details></article><article class="card card-pad stack"><p class="eyebrow">Still need us?</p><h2 class="heading-card-lg">Send a support request</h2><p class="muted">We will never ask for a full payment card, bank password, provider secret, government ID, or identity document.</p><a class="button button-gold" href="<?= $url('contact.index', [], '/contact') ?>">Contact support</a><a class="button button-ghost" href="mailto:<?= $esc((string)($app['support_email']??'support@lordfunion.dev')) ?>"><?= $esc((string)($app['support_email']??'support@lordfunion.dev')) ?></a></article></div></section>
